  "prompt": "What would happen if your visa to live and work in Dubai was about to expire, you'd paid any debts but you had no money to fly home?",
  "response": "In Dubai, if your visa is expiring and you can't afford a flight home, you could:\n\n1. Contact your embassy/consulate for potential assistance\n2. Seek help from your employer if you were working\n3. Request a temporary deportation visa from immigration authorities\n4. Potentially get a travel loan or assistance from local charities\n5. In worst case, you might be held in a deportation center until arrangements are made\n\nThe UAE generally tries to help people in difficult situations, but specific outcomes can vary depending on individual circumstances.",
